headline: IFF to Release First Quarter 2025 Results on May 6, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, April 14, 2025--IFF (NYSE:IFF) today announced that it will release its first quarter 2025 earnings results following the market close on Tuesday, May 6, 2025. The management team will host a live webcast on Wednesday, May 7, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss results and outlook with the investor community.

headline: International Flavors to Boost Presence in Mexico With New Facility
summary: IFF plans to consolidate the majority of its business operations in Mexico at a new site within the Tecnoparque business complex to meet customer demand in the region.
